               <p>Cross-examined by MR. PHILLIPS. Q. The prisoner is your cousin - A. Yes. He went to sea, and returned in distress. We missed some victuals at the same time.</p>
               <p>MR. PHILLIPS. My Lord, the prisoner wishes to plead Guilty to this charge, and throw himself on your mercy.</p>
